#: {{uxi|ceb|'''may pagka'''tabian si Antonio|Antonio is '''somewhat''' talkative}}

====Usage notes====
* In contrast to {{m|ceb|aduna}} and {{m|ceb|anaa}}, which behave as verbs and could thus take [[postpositive]] enclitics, [[may]] is a particle and is used immediately before the word modified.
*: {{uxi|ceb|'''may''' sakyanan siya|she '''has''' a car}}
*: {{uxi|ceb|'''may''' siya sakyanan|''is ungrammatical''}}

